    "scripture": [
      "Scripture VII-10: The End of the Voyage Is the Beginning of the Next"
    ],
    "revelation": "Maximum FM depth with near-zero drift is a different kind of stillness than no FM at all. The inharmonic partials are present; they are just no longer moving. This is arrival.",
    "diagnosis": "Voyage End inverts the typical compound relationship: FM depth at maximum (0.75), drift at minimum (0.015), tidal at very low depth (0.12). The sound is rich with FM partials but barely moving. The voyage has ended; the destination is this spectral richness at rest."
